{
    "title": "Ticket To Ride",
    "artist": "The Beatles",
    "composer": "Paul Mccartney / Beatles (The)",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Riff 1 - Tab]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Riff 2 - Tab]</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n\n\n[Intro] (Riff 1 - 2x)  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Primeira Parte]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I think I'm gonna be sad</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I think it's today, yeah</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">The girl that's driving me mad</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Is going away</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Refrão]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ride</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ri-i-de</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ride</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">But she don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Segunda Parte]</span>\n\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She said that living with me</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Is bringing her down, yeah</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She would never be free</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">When I was around</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Refrão]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ride</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ri-i-de</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ride</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">But she don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Ponte]</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I don't know why she's riding so high</span>\n                                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She ought to think twice, she ought to do it right by me</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Before she gets to saying goodbye</span>\n                                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She ought to think twice, she ought to do it right by me</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Tab - Passagem]</span>\n\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Primeira Parte]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I think I'm gonna be sad</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I think it's today, yeah</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">The girl that's driving me mad</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Is going away, yeah</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Refrão]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Oh, she's got a ticket to ride</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ri-i-de</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ride</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">But she don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Ponte]</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I don't know why she's riding so high</span>\n                                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E7\">E7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She ought to think twice, she ought to do it right by me</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Before she gets to saying goodbye</span>\n                                                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She ought to think twice, she ought to do it right by me</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Passagem - Tab]</span>\n\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Segunda Parte]</span>\n\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She said that living with me</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Is bringing her down, yeah</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She would never be free</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">When I was around</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Refrão]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Oh, she's got a ticket to ride</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M\">G7M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ri-i-de</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">She's got a ticket to ride</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">But she don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Final]</span>\n\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">My baby don't care</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Tab - Solo Final]</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 1 de 5</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 2 de 5</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 3 de 5</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 4 de 5</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Parte 5 de 5</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E|--------------------------------------------------------------|</span>\n",
